# Schuyler's user-global gitignore excludes .claude/ entirely, but this repo
# vendors the book's writing-voice skill there and remote sessions need it from
# a clone. Re-include only .claude/skills/; everything else under .claude/
# (settings.local.json etc.) stays ignored.
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/settings.json
*.log
*.csv
